cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is about person search, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with the refinement of bounding boxes, which is related to object detection, a topic that falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
